data.description: Nestled in Ashford Grove, this inviting 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home offers a spacious layout for modern living in Tomball. The floor plan includes a Formal Dining Room, Huge Game Room, AND a Study! The Kitchen is open to the living room making it great for entertaining. Upstairs you'll find a generously sized Game Room perfect for a pool table & w/ plenty of space for a seating area as well. There's a separate study for your home office too. The corner lot provides privacy & a large fenced backyard that can accommodate an inground pool &/or play equipment. For added convenience & versatility, one of the upstairs bedrooms has a private ensuite bath, ideal for in-laws or guests. Zoned to Klein ISD, this home promises an excellent education for students. Moreover, its location places you in proximity to numerous amenities, ensuring a vibrant and convenient lifestyle.   New HVAC system in 2021. Room sizes are approximate.
